title: Village Life- 3 bed /1.5 bath- Lindstrom- Lake views /Fenced Yard
posting_body: ['Lindstrom Cottage-  3 Bedroom 1.5 bath, September 1st in Duplex', 'AVAILABLE: September 1st ( 9/1)', '*HOUSE- 1300 sq ft- 3 bedrooms- Owners Suite, Lake View bed, and Village View Bed- 1 Bath, 1 common area bathroom, Dishwasher and Air Conditioning,  (there is a common space entry- with an extra bathroom and laundry).', 'There is a guest cottage that is neighboring to this, but this house is private).', '*LOCATION- Heart of the lovely Village of Lindstrom', '*STYLE- Cottage, newly renovated (built in 1908)', '*HEAT- Forced Air Furnace', '*A/C- Window only', '*LAUNDRY- washer/dryer (free)', '*YARD-', 'Fenced in Yard', '*NEIGHBORHOOD-', 'The backyard goes into one of the best coffee shops in the state- Northwoods Roasterie, there is a bike path that brings you to Center City or Chisago, Walk to downtown, down to North Lindstrom lake or Beach Park at Middle Lindstrom Lake', '*PARKING: free- off street parking', '*PETS- $25/mo pet fee per pet+ no aggressive dog breeds (no dogs in carpeted areas)', '...', 'RENT: $1700/mo', 'UTILITIES:', 'You: Gas + $75/mo flat fee (electric/garbage/sewer/water; internet)', 'LEASE- 12 months, 1st month rent + security deposit of $1700 to secure the lease', '...', '**YOU- Message w/your full name +phone # + email + best time to call and a little about yourself, can also send you a video tour prior to a showing)', '***SHOWINGS: BY Appointment on Thursday evenings and Saturday Afternoons', '...', '**YOU- Take into consideration via Individual Assesment- credit score (if affects ability to pay rent), criminal record, rental record- paid on time/not creating damage, # of inahabitants (< 5),income to pay rent- 3x rent, but review opportunity to be able to pay.', '9 month minimum lease.', 'Individual Assesment (will review your supplemental information)- incident surroundings, time elapsed and age when it happened.', 'DO NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers', '...', 'Keywords: Lake , Chisago, Village, September 1, September 15, October 1 , 9/1 , 9/15, 10/1']
